montana scher experimedia home experimedia digital humanities product design montana scher montana scher is a graphic designer for the experimedia group she is not from montana and has unfortunately never visited the state that took her name born and raised in beautiful santa barbara ca she loves frolicking in the ocean and wandering up mountain trails she is currently an undeclared sophomore at stanford university dabbling in subjects like mechanical engineering art studio and computer science possibly fusing all of her interests into a science technology and society major her passion for problem solving and smart beautiful design has lead to her love of gluten free baking a good challenging puzzle and endless adobe illustrator sessions search this site navigation groups recent posts user login login
